oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry stars Justin Tubb and Marion Worth at the High School Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black on yellow) Hatch poster announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Justin Tubb, Marion Worth, LaVonne Lear, Grover Ruwe, the Cantrells, and Gary Van at the Lincoln High School Auditorium on July 3. Poster features metal photoplates of Justin Tubb, Marion Worth, LaVonne Lear, Grover Ruwe, the Cantrells, and Gary Van.
